    <h1>Let's <span>talk</span>.</h1>
    <p>Questions, bug reports, feature ideas — all welcome. For bugs and feature requests, <a href="{{ site.githubUrl }}/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">open a GitHub issue</a>. For everything else, email is the fastest way to reach us.</p>
  </section>

